citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4:15 pm on March
15, 2022.
Inspector knocked on the door, rang the doorbell, left two voicemail messages and waited approx. 45 minutes at the
residence.
End Section
